{"tid":338081,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"［隨便台］[開CAM開台]香港DBD排名第一台主開台","createTime":"2017-07-28T01:00:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T09:03:53.000Z","uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e75ea173c79cbc3394d3701fe9e3806d0d119ddf","tid":338081,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:00:47.000Z","msg":"Twitch : <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/justin_yu_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fjustin_yu_1&d=0Rc1niVKHQez1KxBgjsGc%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d31d8992\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/justin_yu_1</a><br />\nTwitch桌面app : <a href=\"https://app.twitch.tv/servers/Lz96Me\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fapp.twitch.tv%2Fservers%2FLz96Me&d=0Rc1niVKHQez1KxBgjsGc%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=dcbbb224\" target=\"_blank\">https://app.twitch.tv/servers/Lz96Me</a><br />\nYoutube : <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFNLF-gKhVFb_AeUzQsD-aQ/featured\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCFNLF-gKhVFb_AeUzQsD-aQ%2Ffeatured&d=0Rc1niVKHQez1KxBgjsGc%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b0ce4c65\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCFNLF-gKhVFb_AeUzQsD-aQ/featured</a><br />\nFacebook : <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/隨便台-355532761277816/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%E9%9A%A8%E4%BE%BF%E5%8F%B0-355532761277816%2F&d=0Rc1niVKHQez1KxBgjsGc%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5de7a90e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/隨便台-355532761277816/</a><br />\nLINE : <a href=\"https://line.me/R/ti/p/@snp0516q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fline.me%2FR%2Fti%2Fp%2F%40snp0516q&d=0Rc1niVKHQez1KxBgjsGc%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=36b933f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://line.me/R/ti/p/@snp0516q</a><br />\nInstagram : <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/justin_yu_1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fjustin_yu_1%2F&d=0Rc1niVKHQez1KxBgjsGc%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=69b2d15a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/justin_yu_1/</a><br />\nTwitter : <a href=\"https://twitter.com/justin_yu_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fjustin_yu_1&d=0Rc1niVKHQez1KxBgjsGc%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=a89535fa\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/justin_yu_1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/FR9gM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FFR9gM.png&h=28783526&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDead by daylight呢隻GAME,係一隻4 VS 1既GAME,4個人類一邊維修發電機一邊避開個殺手,維修夠發電機開大門走佬;玩殺手既就係盡量殺D人,唔俾佢地走到佬<br />\n可惜,呢隻GAME,外國好多人玩,偏偏淨係香港冇人玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好多係身在外國既香港人,都同我講呢隻GAME外國係勁多人玩,普遍香港人個STEAM都設定係香港,所以香港人買左,馬上開GAME,幾乎係肯定冇場,因為香港SER根本冇人,已經真係有玩開GAME既人,都已經轉哂SER去其他國家玩,而依家最多人既SER而又唔會太LAG既地方,係轉去台灣泰國日本韓國呢D地方既SER玩<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/HdDRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FHdDRQ.jpg&h=300ec0a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TKEUxPYvRfI?list=PLSow1H3Pe09MwgV9rjsjfYx4FiIKrNU4a\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTKEUxPYvRfI%3Flist%3DPLSow1H3Pe09MwgV9rjsjfYx4FiIKrNU4a&d=0Rc1niVKHQez1KxBgjsGc%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=2a892822\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TKEUxPYvRfI?list=PLSow1H3Pe09MwgV9rjsjfYx4FiIKrNU4a</a><br />\n由於係香港開CAM開台而又玩呢隻GAME既人,係得我一個台,所以呢隻GAME官方果邊都俾左呢一件twitch台台主先有既SKIN我<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/S1eUb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FS1eUb.jpg&h=8bd1a985&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/S1bmP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FS1bmP.jpg&h=3b0c8436&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/vHoXA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FvHoXA.jpg&h=1fb87b30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n下面呢個係隨便台Official LINE群,有咩突發消息,開台通知,我都會係呢度公布<br />\n<img src=\"http://qr-official.line.me/L/aqio2VXZLo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqr-official.line.me%2FL%2Faqio2VXZLo.png&h=03fd5638&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07b3e5960470937df8836718cef205f82ece2d23","tid":338081,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:00:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804daf9a851453f41181ee99e785f2b9b20d350e","tid":338081,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:01:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7771cd44d454531e5709d0df5cd6192be613f22","tid":338081,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d48926760e6376807fa8c5204a4ae3575682a2","tid":338081,"uid":89382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-28T01:21:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/no